snippet.title: Johnny Depp And Amber Heard Documentary Is A MUST Watch... Here's Why!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp And Amber Heard Documentary Is A MUST Watch... Here's Why! 

Welcome back to Show Focus. Disney+ is rumored to be launching a new documentary that will focus on telling the romantic timeline of former couple Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. On this channel right now, we present Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's relationship breakdown to be the focus of a new documentary...here’s what we know!

The new Disney+ documentary will have a title of Johnny vs Amber. It will be a two-part documentary special produced by Disney+ in partnership with Optomen. Stick around and watch this video for more details regarding the story of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's relationship breakdown to be the focus of a new documentary...here’s what we know!
